    "path": "/organizations/linear-setup.html",
    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>You can integrate with Linear in order to sync information between your HackerOne report and your Linear issue.</p>\n<p>To integrate with Linear:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Integrations.</strong></li>\n<li>Click the <strong>Connect with Linear link.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAANElEQVQI16WM0QoAEBTF/P/PUm640Y6Qd2W1t7WQrGkBbF+5bR+o+rE4Cr9D7yhmFA0lQxM1Y5544CRO0QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-1\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-1\"\n        src=\"/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/0b533/linear-setup-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/fac75/linear-setup-1.png 125w,\n/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/63868/linear-setup-1.png 250w,\n/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/0b533/linear-setup-1.png 500w,\n/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/1d69c/linear-setup-1.png 750w,\n/static/1cb00ba6591c0d1431f9a8bc89d587ef/73fd0/linear-setup-1.png 793w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Click the <strong>Set up new integration</strong> button.</li>\n<li>Enter <strong>Name</strong> and <strong>Description</strong> for your new integration and click <strong>Next.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 93.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-2\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-2\"\n        src=\"/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/0b533/linear-setup-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/fac75/linear-setup-2.png 125w,\n/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/63868/linear-setup-2.png 250w,\n/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/0b533/linear-setup-2.png 500w,\n/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/1d69c/linear-setup-2.png 750w,\n/static/8230da99ca61af47affd56c26d015dd4/9cab2/linear-setup-2.png 864w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Navigate to the Linear API settings of Linear by going to <strong>Settings > API</strong> and add a new <strong>Personal API key</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-3\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-3\"\n        src=\"/static/a9a1a29168bc125639c2bb75ece0c305/0b533/linear-setup-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a9a1a29168bc125639c2bb75ece0c305/fac75/linear-setup-3.png 125w,\n/static/a9a1a29168bc125639c2bb75ece0c305/63868/linear-setup-3.png 250w,\n/static/a9a1a29168bc125639c2bb75ece0c305/0b533/linear-setup-3.png 500w,\n/static/a9a1a29168bc125639c2bb75ece0c305/f6386/linear-setup-3.png 686w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Copy the generated key and save it somewhere. <strong>This key is shown only once</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-4\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-4\"\n        src=\"/static/d954b14349529f9c7762d1e700991b48/0b533/linear-setup-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d954b14349529f9c7762d1e700991b48/fac75/linear-setup-4.png 125w,\n/static/d954b14349529f9c7762d1e700991b48/63868/linear-setup-4.png 250w,\n/static/d954b14349529f9c7762d1e700991b48/0b533/linear-setup-4.png 500w,\n/static/d954b14349529f9c7762d1e700991b48/74866/linear-setup-4.png 668w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>\n<p>Navigate back to HackerOne and click <strong>Add a new account</strong> in the Linear authentication window.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Enter your API key from step 6 in the <strong>Create a new authentication window</strong> in the <strong>Master token</strong> field and click <strong>Create.</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-5\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-5\"\n        src=\"/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/0b533/linear-setup-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/fac75/linear-setup-5.png 125w,\n/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/63868/linear-setup-5.png 250w,\n/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/0b533/linear-setup-5.png 500w,\n/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/1d69c/linear-setup-5.png 750w,\n/static/737c66b9f310cb75db8b663b5a5d4f05/d7542/linear-setup-5.png 810w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>Configure which Linear Team and Project (optional) you'd like to escalate HackerOne reports to in the <strong>Linear Team and Project</strong> window and click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-6\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-6\"\n        src=\"/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/0b533/linear-setup-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/fac75/linear-setup-6.png 125w,\n/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/63868/linear-setup-6.png 250w,\n/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/0b533/linear-setup-6.png 500w,\n/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/1d69c/linear-setup-6.png 750w,\n/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/00d43/linear-setup-6.png 1000w,\n/static/987b85dbfce203bcdbeb75de48f96123/1c1a4/linear-setup-6.png 1046w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li>Select the HackerOne fields you want to map to the corresponding Linear fields. Alternatively, enter any text using <a href=\"/organizations/integration-variables.html\">integration variables</a>. Click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-7\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-7\"\n        src=\"/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/0b533/linear-setup-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/fac75/linear-setup-7.png 125w,\n/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/63868/linear-setup-7.png 250w,\n/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/0b533/linear-setup-7.png 500w,\n/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/1d69c/linear-setup-7.png 750w,\n/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/00d43/linear-setup-7.png 1000w,\n/static/44e808074725afd5dd260abd4b197397/20751/linear-setup-7.png 1037w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: You can manually set the mapping to a single field or combination of fields from the <a href=\"/organizations/integration-variables.html\">integration variables</a>. For example: <code>{{triage_summary}} \\\\ Link: {{report_link}} \\\\ Date: {{submission_date}} \\\\ Reporter: {{reporter_name}} \\\\ Weakness: {{weakness}}</code> Would create a combination of the triage summary, a link to the report, the submission date, the reporter name, the weakness of their report and map that to a single field.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"11\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select the Linear Priorities you want to map to the corresponding HackerOne Severities. This enables the right priority to be set when escalating a HackerOne report to Linear. Click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-integration-10\"\n        title=\"linear-integration-10\"\n        src=\"/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/0b533/linear-integration-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/fac75/linear-integration-10.png 125w,\n/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/63868/linear-integration-10.png 250w,\n/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/0b533/linear-integration-10.png 500w,\n/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/1d69c/linear-integration-10.png 750w,\n/static/871fee74d758bc7450dd28d2739ad831/227ba/linear-integration-10.png 769w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"12\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select which actions in HackerOne you'd like to post to Linear in the <strong>Select HackerOne to Linear events</strong> window. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Comment added</td>\n<td>When someone comments on a report, post an update on the associated Linear issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>State changed</td>\n<td>When someone changes the state of a report, post an update on the associated Linear issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Reward changed</td>\n<td>When someone awards or suggests a bounty and/or bonus, post an update on the associated Linear issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Assignee changed</td>\n<td>When someone assigns a user/group to a report, post an update on the associated Linear issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Disclosure</td>\n<td>When disclosure is requested or a report becomes public, post an update on the associated Linear issue.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-integration-8\"\n        title=\"linear-integration-8\"\n        src=\"/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/0b533/linear-integration-8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/fac75/linear-integration-8.png 125w,\n/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/63868/linear-integration-8.png 250w,\n/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/0b533/linear-integration-8.png 500w,\n/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/1d69c/linear-integration-8.png 750w,\n/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/00d43/linear-integration-8.png 1000w,\n/static/9170ad95e7a83346526ae0c0c5bbaa62/1ff84/linear-integration-8.png 1040w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Click <strong>Next</strong>.</p>\n<ol start=\"13\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select which Linear actions you'd like to post onto HackerOne in the <strong>Select Linear to HackerOne events</strong> window. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Status changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes status.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Closed issue status</td>\n<td>Resolve the report when an issue is closed with the selected status.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Comment added</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when someone comments on an issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Assignee changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes assignee.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Priority changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes priority.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-integration-9\"\n        title=\"linear-integration-9\"\n        src=\"/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/0b533/linear-integration-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/fac75/linear-integration-9.png 125w,\n/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/63868/linear-integration-9.png 250w,\n/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/0b533/linear-integration-9.png 500w,\n/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/1d69c/linear-integration-9.png 750w,\n/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/00d43/linear-integration-9.png 1000w,\n/static/cfa4f5b86f6939c6a2f5bba06ca56be6/76823/linear-integration-9.png 1038w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Click <strong>Next</strong>.</p>\n<ol start=\"14\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> If you have configured Linear actions to be synchronized to HackerOne in step 13, you will need to configure a webhook in Linear. Copy the <strong>Webhook Public URL</strong> that is shown in the <strong>Workflow URLs</strong> screen.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-8\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-8\"\n        src=\"/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/0b533/linear-setup-8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/fac75/linear-setup-8.png 125w,\n/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/63868/linear-setup-8.png 250w,\n/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/0b533/linear-setup-8.png 500w,\n/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/1d69c/linear-setup-8.png 750w,\n/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/00d43/linear-setup-8.png 1000w,\n/static/4de85ed07847162fdf4b207bab2780b7/5819f/linear-setup-8.png 1042w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Navigate to the API settings in Linear by going to <strong>Settings > API</strong> and create a new <strong>Webhook</strong>.</li>\n<li>Give the webhook a descriptive label and enter the Webhook Public URL into the <strong>URL</strong> field.</li>\n<li>Save the <strong>Signing secret</strong> for use later.</li>\n<li>Check the <strong>Issues</strong> and <strong>Issue comments</strong> events in the <strong>Data change events</strong> section.</li>\n<li>Finally set the <strong>Teams</strong> to <strong>Custom</strong>, and select only the team you have selected in step 9.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Create webhook</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 160%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-9\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-9\"\n        src=\"/static/b272c385fc28f6dfa7234696dd0397ec/0b533/linear-setup-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b272c385fc28f6dfa7234696dd0397ec/fac75/linear-setup-9.png 125w,\n/static/b272c385fc28f6dfa7234696dd0397ec/63868/linear-setup-9.png 250w,\n/static/b272c385fc28f6dfa7234696dd0397ec/0b533/linear-setup-9.png 500w,\n/static/b272c385fc28f6dfa7234696dd0397ec/748f4/linear-setup-9.png 656w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Copy the Signing Secret into the <strong>Linear webhook secret</strong> field.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-10\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-10\"\n        src=\"/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/0b533/linear-setup-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/fac75/linear-setup-10.png 125w,\n/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/63868/linear-setup-10.png 250w,\n/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/0b533/linear-setup-10.png 500w,\n/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/1d69c/linear-setup-10.png 750w,\n/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/00d43/linear-setup-10.png 1000w,\n/static/3da70ba565626a8ffd22949d06a59229/7a1fb/linear-setup-10.png 1030w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"18\">\n<li>Click <strong>Finish</strong>. Once the screen disappears, click <strong>Enable</strong> to enable the integration.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.400000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAiklEQVQY042PSwrCQBQE5/6nEC/gLXQlLgXBhYohColOksl7mV8JhrgSY0NBL4qGNlVtuVxv9JrImXfyVGbyzTPiHPZRo9IhfY+qfuSfpHEsnCraxZp2ucGtdphaHY142i4gGogxzo9NANEKui8YDiX+eMdsqzPF09I0HhnC35fzKJKALmWGIJADLzW5OSAIbUsxAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"linear-setup-11\"\n        title=\"linear-setup-11\"\n        src=\"/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/0b533/linear-setup-11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/fac75/linear-setup-11.png 125w,\n/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/63868/linear-setup-11.png 250w,\n/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/0b533/linear-setup-11.png 500w,\n/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/1d69c/linear-setup-11.png 750w,\n/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/00d43/linear-setup-11.png 1000w,\n/static/e3231e8ddd6ba1c686ae077acab306d0/d3f96/linear-setup-11.png 1093w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>You're all set! Now that you've finished setting up the Linear integration, you can <a href=\"/organizations/linear-integration.html#creating-a-Linear-issue\">create Linear issues</a> right from your HackerOne report.</p>\n<h3 id=\"multiple-integrations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#multiple-integrations\" aria-label=\"multiple integrations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Multiple integrations</h3>\n<p>If you have multiple HackerOne programs, you can integrate them to the same Linear instance. Steps 5-6 can be omitted for each subsequent program you need to add an integration for.</p>\n<h3 id=\"multiple-linear-instances-per-program\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#multiple-linear-instances-per-program\" aria-label=\"multiple linear instances per program permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Multiple Linear instances per Program</h3>\n<p>This feature is available for <strong>Enterprise programs only</strong>. If you want to integrate the same program to multiple Linear instances, you can follow all the steps above for each integration.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/organizations/linear-setup.html","id":"organizations/linear-setup","title":"Linear Setup","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Multiple integrations"},{"value":"Multiple Linear instances per Program"}]}},"pageContext":{}},
